name: Babies "R" Us
overview:
We feature an unparalleled selection of cribs, furniture, car seats, strollers, formula, diapers, bedding, clothing and toys, as well as an array of unique gift ideas. Expectant parents consistently rate our Babies“R”Us Registry number one – and for good reason. Registrants can take advantage of the unmatched assortment of innovative and exclusive baby products, as well as expertise provided, whether they are registering in-store or online.

We also offer a number of convenient services and amenities in our stores, such as a Mother’s Room for baby care, Stork Parking spaces conveniently located near the front of the store for expectant moms and a Special Orders desk.
